        "notes": "You see A kind, nervous looking young recruit whose outfit is just a but too big for him. \n\n\"Oh, hello, the Sergeant will be here in just a moment... he's in the loo.\"\n\nCan help with\nA kind word and quiet help; directions to the Guild or the apothecary; the small truths Dorran will not say.\n\nReveals if asked\nThe Guild is desperate for hands; contracts have gone badly and heroes keep not coming back; the city is more frightened than it admits.",
